snippet.title: Jeff Gordon XS Racing  - Track Tour - The Accelerator
snippet.description: Built inside a nuclear plant area, it is no stranger to danger. It is an intense track with some distractions that can throw you off-course. Starting off with a big hairpin turn, it leads you to a tunnel where one road closes, opening a detour to another series of track, leading to an alternate nuclear route where a big 90 degree turn comes out of nowhere, enticing drivers to exercise extreme caution. Keep in mind that this heart-pounding race course, is not for the faint of heart.
